Breadcrumbs

University Library


Collections


Digital Images & Media






Digital Images & Media
Digital image collections, online exhibits and databases.





            Digital image resources
          Heading link



 
Copy link









                            UIC Digital Collections
                    

                Digitized materials from UIC Collections and University Archives.  Digitized documents, letters, media, audio, video.
            









                            UIC Library Digital Exhibits
                    

                In-depth explorations from our Special Collections & University Archives.  Media, documents, interviews and more.
            









                            Explore Chicago Collections
                    

                Chicago history and culture from libraries, museums and archives across the city.  Images and archival guides.
            









                            Digital Public Library of America
                    

                Images, documents and letters from libraries and museums throughout the U.S. in a wide range of subject areas.
            









                            Europeana
                    

                Images, documents and media from libraries and museums in Europe
            









                            ArtStor
                    

                Over 2.5 million images from museums, artists, libraries and archives.  Arts, architecture, humanities, social sciences.
            









                            Illinois Digital Heritage Hub
                    

                Brings together unique digital cultural heritage resources from across Illinois: photographs, manuscripts, books, audio recordings, and videos from a network of more than 150 partners.
            










